column2: SELECT u.up_name as [name], # + cast (x.objId as varchar (#) ) + #+ cast (x.objId as varchar (#) ) + # as objID, p.ra, p.dec, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field, dbo.fPhotoTypeN (p.type) as type, p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z, s.specObjID, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberID, s.z, s.zConf, s.fiberMag_u, s.fiberMag_g, s.fiberMag_r, s.fiberMag_i, s.fiberMag_z, sli.name, sli.ew, sli.ewErr, sli.mag, sli.magErr, sli.waveMin, sli.waveMax, sli.z, sli.sn, sli.specobjID FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN PhotoTag p ON p.objID = x.objID JOIN SpecObjAll s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID JOIN SpecLineIndex sli ON p.SpecObjID = sli.SpecObjID ORDER by x.up_id
